title: Storm Doris claims its second victim after death of man whose car was struck by a falling tree in last week’s high winds
text:
Opinion SECOND DORIS DEATH Storm Doris claims its second victim after death of man whose car was struck by a falling tree in last week’s high winds 
The man, in his 80s, has sadly passed away after being caught up in last week's high winds By ELLIE FLYNN
